29#include <ar.h>
30#include <libelf.h>
31
32#include "_libelf.h"
33
34__RCSID("$NetBSD: elf_shnum.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
35ELFTC_VCSID("Id: elf_shnum.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");
36
37static int
38_libelf_getshdrnum(Elf *e, size_t *shnum)
39{
40 void *eh;
41 int ec;
42
43 if (e == NULL || e->e_kind != ELF_K_ELF ||
44 ((ec = e->e_class) != ELFCLASS32 && ec != ELFCLASS64)) {
45 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
46 return (-1);
47 }
48
49 if ((eh = _libelf_ehdr(e, ec, 0)) == NULL)
50 return (-1);
51
52 *shnum = e->e_u.e_elf.e_nscn;
53
54 return (0);
55}
56
57int
58elf_getshdrnum(Elf *e, size_t *shnum)
59{
60 return (_libelf_getshdrnum(e, shnum));
61}
62
63/* Deprecated API. */
64int
65elf_getshnum(Elf *e, size_t *shnum)
66{
67 return (_libelf_getshdrnum(e, shnum) >= 0);
68}
